videos.description: Coming off a fast break, the Bears' Davion Mitchell sends a bounce pass to Devonte Bandoo, who finishes with a powerful dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor's Bandoo stuffs the rim with the 2-handed jam) 2019/11/5

videos.headline: Baylor's Bandoo stuffs the rim with the 2-handed jam

videos.description: MaCio Teague shakes off his defender to get the ball to an open Jared Butler for another Baylor 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Baylor's Teague finds the open Butler for a 3) 2019/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Teague finds the open Butler for a 3

videos.description: After getting the defensive rebound, MaCio Teague runs it up the court, smoothly circles the defense, and finishes with a layup.
